column3: this (the tailwind) feels real easy. I’m going to hate it on the way home.
oh, emotional state. Hasn’t changed since I got on the bike – I don’t believe. I haven’t felt any concern.
noted that he felt too self-conscious to talk while ‘guy was standing there’
there is a car behind me, which is probably annoyed with where I am, but as I explained before, between parked cars, driveways, other roads – I feel this is the most safest place.
